title: 869. Matt Rhule Firing, Big Week 5 Games, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
itunes:title: 869. Matt Rhule Firing, Big Week 5 Games, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and all the action from Week 5 of the NFL season. The guys start by reacting to the news of the Panthers firing head coach Matt Rhule and look back at college to NFL head coaching hires. Next, the trio break down the big 3 games from Sunday. After, the group hit on their 8 takeaways from Week 5. Following that, the guys each give a standout rookie and also their favorite performance. Then, the trio focus on how the Saints are using tight end Taysom Hill in a creative way.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
